data.description: Welcome home! This spacious ranch home has absolutely gorgeous curb appeal. Professionally landscaped with automatic sprinkler system for the front and backyard. The home sits on a large lot that also has a gated separate area for your Recreational Vehicle with a 30-amp external outlet to power it up! Enter this beautiful home to be greeted by an open concept floorplan. There are many windows throughout with custom cut window blinds. Features on the main level include a tiled Entry, Formal Dining Room with large window, vaulted ceilings, gas fireplace and an amazing view out the back patio of the Rocky Mountains. Beautiful kitchen with tiled floors, an island/breakfast bar with extra built in cabinetry for extra storage, beautiful cabinetry with hardware, deep farm sink, pantry, stainless steel appliances and sunny eating space to enjoy your informal meals. The main floor Master Suite has custom painted ceiling & fan, crown molding, barn door entry to walk in closet, private bathroom with double vanity, corner jetted tub and walk-in shower & closet. Laundry Room is conveniently located between Entry and Garage. The Basement features a large Family Room with dry bar area, 4th bedroom with walk-in closet and a 3/4 Bath with walk-in shower. Check out the wonderful hobby room with built-in cabinets, large countertop and pegboard for all your crafting supplies! There is also a utility sink in the unfinished basement. Backyard is great for entertaining. Best of all no HOA.
